Gerrit has been installed.

To enable Gerrit during boot-time add the following line to /etc/rc.conf:

	gerrit_enable="YES"

Once Gerrit is first started it will initialize itself and then start up.

In order to access your Gerrit instance open up a browser at port 8080, e.g.:

	http://example.org:8080/

For more information about Gerrit, please check the online documentation:

WWW:	http://gerrit-documentation.googlecode.com/svn/Documentation/2.2.0/index.html
